dc_description_s: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Bayfield County in 2019.[This layer contains public land data based on 2019 assessment codes in Bayfield County.Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Downloada
